Description_lang: Tiger Palm has a $s1% chance to deal $s2% of normal damage and reduce the remaining cooldown of your Brews by ${$s3/1000} additional sec.

description_blz.en_US: Tiger Palm has a 50% chance to deal 200% of normal damage and reduce the remaining cooldown of your Brews by 1 additional sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Palma del tigre tiene un 50% de probabilidad de infligir un 200% de daño normal y reducir 1 s más el tiempo de reutilización restante de tus brebajes.
description_blz.pt_BR: Palma do Tigre tem 50% de chance de causar 200% do dano normal e reduzir a recarga restante das suas Cervejas em mais 1 s.
description_blz.de_DE: 'Tigerklaue' hat eine Chance von 50%, 200% des normalen Schadens zu verursachen und die verbleibende Abklingzeit Eurer Gebräue um zusätzlich 1 Sek. zu verringern.
description_blz.en_GB: Tiger Palm has a 50% chance to deal 200% of normal damage and reduce the remaining cooldown of your Brews by 1 additional sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Palma del tigre tiene un 50% de probabilidad de infligir un 200% del daño normal y de reducir 1 s más el tiempo de reutilización restante de tus brebajes.
description_blz.fr_FR: Paume du tigre a 50% de chances d’infliger 200% des dégâts normaux et de réduire de 1 s supplémentaire le temps de recharge restant de vos breuvages.
description_blz.it_IT: Palmo della Tigre ha una probabilità del 50% di infliggere il 200% dei danni normali e ridurre il tempo di recupero restante delle tue Birre di 1 s aggiuntivi.

description_blz.ko_KR: 범의 장풍이 50%의 확률로 일반 공격력의 200%에 해당하는 피해를 입히고, 맥주 능력의 남은 재사용 대기시간을 추가로 1초만큼 감소시킵니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 虎掌有50%機率造成200%的額外傷害，並可讓絕釀剩餘的冷卻時間額外縮短1秒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 猛虎掌有50%几率造成200%的普通伤害，并使你的酒类技能剩余的冷却时间额外缩短1秒。
